-- Enabling the replication database
use master
exec sp_replicationdboption @dbname = N'CoreIssue', @optname = N'publish', @value = N'true'
GO

exec [CoreIssue].sys.sp_addlogreader_agent @job_login = null, @job_password = null, @publisher_security_mode = 1
GO
-- Adding the transactional publication
use [CoreIssue]
exec sp_addpublication @publication = N'Trans_PUB_CoreissueReportPUB', @description = N'Transactional publication of database ''CoreIssue'' from Publisher ''MUM-DB01''.', @sync_method = N'concurrent', @retention = 0, @allow_push = N'true', @allow_pull = N'true', @allow_anonymous = N'true', @enabled_for_internet = N'false', @snapshot_in_defaultfolder = N'true', @compress_snapshot = N'false', @ftp_port = 21, @ftp_login = N'anonymous', @allow_subscription_copy = N'false', @add_to_active_directory = N'false', @repl_freq = N'continuous', @status = N'active', @independent_agent = N'true', @immediate_sync = N'true', @allow_sync_tran = N'false', @autogen_sync_procs = N'false', @allow_queued_tran = N'false', @allow_dts = N'false', @replicate_ddl = 1, @allow_initialize_from_backup = N'false', @enabled_for_p2p = N'false', @enabled_for_het_sub = N'false'
